::DarkMouse::

She looked up fromher note and at Quickstrike.
"Huh? Oh..uh, yeah sure thing commander.  I think I have most of the figures 
I need to start drilling in these two back caves to make the escape tunnels 
that you spoke of.  I mentioned to Megatron that you had mentioned this and 
was acting under you suggestion. I will need help managing the lazar to make 
the tunnels.  If it pleases you, I would need your help on this project."

------Original Message---------
From: Talon Harvilicz  <wilddance_mare@h...>
Date: Fri Jun 23, 2000 4:27pm
Subject: Neo Beast Wars


Quickstrike:


Quickstrike looked around the cave, eyeing the progress. He made a count of 
the bots inside their new base, and thought of what could be done. As Dark 
Mouse said, they had scanners, auto-guns, and a few escape routes were on 
their way. He walked up to the mouse's position, getting a little bored with 
being the overseerer.

"Help you wit' anythin'?" he asked her.
